Feature: TC_01_STAFF - Map Printing by Herd Number E2E Regression Pack

  # Migrated from: "Regression Suite for Map Printing with Herd" (AT-TC-01, 02, 04)
  # URL: Hooks/Config. Username: feature. Password: TestData "Password" col via TD: mechanism.
  # Author : Aniket Pathare | aniket.pathare@government.ie
  # Created: 14-07-2026

  Background:
    Given user on staff login page
    When Staff logs in with the Username "agr11612"
    And Staff opens the "Basic Income Support for Sustainability" application
    And Staff switches to the "Map Printing" tab

  @regression @staff @map-printing @herd @e2e
  Scenario: AT-STAFF-MAP-HERD-E2E-01 - Staff generates maps by herd number and validates required-field errors

    # SECTION 1 : Generate map by herd (single parcel change) - AT-TC-01 (BISSAGL-14969)
    When Staff searches on the Map Printing screen with the following details
      | field      | herdNumber |
      | herdValue  | N106036X   |
      | schemeYear | 2023       |
    And Staff changes the "parcelSelect" multi-option dropdown value
    And Staff selects the following map generation settings
      | mapTypeSelect | Full Color Ortho A4 |
    And Staff clicks the Legend Indicator checkbox
    Then Staff clicks the "Generate map" button

    # SECTION 2 : Herd number required validation - AT-TC-02 (BISSAGL-14968)
    When Staff switches to the "Map Printing" tab
    And Staff clicks the "Search" button
    Then Staff should see the error message "Herd number required."

    # SECTION 3 : Generate map by herd (all parcels) - AT-TC-04 (BISSAGL-14966)
    When Staff searches on the Map Printing screen with the following details
      | field      | herdNumber |
      | herdValue  | N106036X   |
      | schemeYear | 2023       |
    And Staff selects all values in the "parcelSelect" multi-option dropdown
    And Staff selects the following map generation settings
      | mapTypeSelect | Full Color Ortho A4 |
    And Staff clicks the Legend Indicator checkbox
    Then Staff clicks the "Generate map" button


